### Strapi API 測試
### 基礎配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:1337
@apiToken = bd8cdd66daecf5db8dbdfbeccbbf4e4adba0a38834f72a66700e31b1ad5864051a3ede3c0f028aae7621ef3077cc2226ed6e61e8c68c80f58d53d70d2ac64f8c401ca0c004378a8d62480ea78190eb9c505571c1b538f659a4a06e8c39e5a1c39ede18dfb600b11511b4f61c84b9fbe92e77a90340122a79e98d8ef9915fb5f1

### 1. 測試 Strapi 連線
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 測試 API Token 是否有效
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/global
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 測試 Global Single Type - 無 Token (檢查公開權限)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/global
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. 測試 About Single Type - 有 Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. 測試 About Single Type - 無 Token (檢查公開權限)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. 測試 Global Single Type 帶 populate 參數
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/global?populate=*
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. 測試 About Single Type 帶 populate 參數
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=*
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. 更新 Global Single Type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/global
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "siteName": "測試網站名稱 - {{$datetime iso8601}}",
    "siteDescription": "這是測試更新的網站描述"
  }
}

### 9. 更新 About Single Type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "title": "測試關於標題 - {{$datetime iso8601}}"
  }
}

### 10. 測試 Collection Type - Articles (檢查是否有其他內容類型)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. 測試 Collection Type - Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. 測試 Collection Type - Authors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. 測試上傳 API
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/upload/files
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. 檢查 API Token 權限 - 嘗試存取管理端點
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. 測試錯誤端點 (應該返回 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nonexistent
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json